the goonies is a 1985 american adventure comedy film directed by richard donner , who produced with harvey bernhard . the screenplay was written by chris columbus from a story by executive producer steven spielberg . a band of pre-teens who live in the " goon docks " neighborhood of astoria , oregon , attempt to save their homes from demolition , and , in doing so , discover an old spanish map that leads them on an adventure to unearth the long-lost fortune of one-eyed willy , a legendary 17th-century pirate . during the entire adventure , they are chased by a family of criminals , who also want the treasure for themselves . warner bros. released it on june 7 , 1985 , in the united states . the film grossed $ 61.5 million worldwide and has become a cult film .